{
  "name": "AnyBase",
  "version": "1.1",
  "description": "Easily convert any element to base64 encoding, which is a plug-in for developers or artists",
  "permissions": [
    "contextMenus",
    "*://*/*"
  ],
  "background": {
    "scripts": [
      "utils.js",
      "background.js"
    ],
    "persistent": false
  },
  "browser_action": {
    "default_popup": "popup.html",
    "default_title": "display tooltip",
    "default_icon": {
      "16": "images/16.png",
      "32": "images/32.png",
      "48": "images/48.png",
      "128": "images/128.png"
    }
  },
  "icons": {
    "16": "images/16.png",
    "32": "images/32.png",
    "48": "images/48.png",
    "128": "images/128.png"
  },
  "manifest_version": 2
}

简单便捷的实用工具
将你的图片，音频，或者网络资源，快速得转换成base64格式
我们目前只在图片和音频元素上提供快捷菜单，当然，点击插件图标，你可以转换一切你想转换的网络资源